detaileddescription.para: Used for identification of the language. The identification should not be translated. It should be replaced by the name of the language in English using lower-case characters only (e.g. "czech", "japanese", "russian", etc.). It should be equal to the identification used in language.cpp.
The English LaTeX does not use such commands. Because of this the empty string is returned in this implementation.
returns the name of the package that is included by LaTeX
